{"tid":2400022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"比特幣升至近4.5萬美元創新高","createTime":"2021-02-08T14:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T14:54:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90f533efa78b26c91f2e55e5d999272e0699957e","tid":2400022,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:52:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574814-20210208.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574814-20210208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=c8907313\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574814-20210208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fb7fd520\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574814-20210208.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n比特幣曾高見近4.49萬美元創新高，升幅近16%，受到特斯拉(Tesla)大幅投資比特幣消息帶動。<br />\n<br />\n特斯拉較早時表示，上月累計投資15億美元於比特幣，相信其比特幣持倉具有高度流動性。<br />\n<br />\n集團又預期，不久將接受比特幣用作支付購買產品，但需要符合適用法律，而初期範圍有限。"},{"pid":"b043e2cfcd168edee1cc6d65bd0b6b22de7dd324","tid":2400022,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美爆近了"}]}